data.description: Welcome to an exquisite 4-bedroom, 4-bathroom haven of luxury and style, proudly built by New Leaf Homes in 2017(with ALL the UPGRADES) in the prestigious Arcadia Ridge subdivision. Spanning 3,031 square feet across two impressive stories, this home stands as a testament to quality construction, sophisticated style, and thoughtful efficiency.  The home is filled with high-end upgrades, from the gleaming granite countertops to the designer lighting fixtures, showcasing meticulous attention to detail.    The centerpiece of this residence is the dream kitchen, a culinary enthusiast's paradise. Outfitted with top-tier appliances, lavish countertops, and an oversized island, it effortlessly blends into the adjoining dining area and living room, making it perfect for both family gatherings and formal entertainment.   Retreat to the expansive master suite located on the main floor where you will fall in love with the master bath!  Double sinks, soaking tub, and a huge walk in shower that screams elegance!  The home has three additional bedrooms, each thoughtfully designed, providing ample space for family or guests.  Do not miss the grandeur of the second floor's high ceilings and second living space.    Step outside to the backyard, a private retreat (no rear Neighbors) with a beautiful 2 tier deck for outdoor enjoyment, whether you're hosting gatherings or simply basking in the fresh air.  This stunning home has integrated energy-efficient features and smart home technology into this property, ensuring not only luxury but also sustainability.    Arcadia Ridge, known for its natural beauty and serene atmosphere, offers access to parks, walking trails, and top-rated schools, making it an ideal community for families.
